To install metric server
clone the code
>git clone https://github.com/kodekloudhub/kubernetes-metrics-server.git

To create metric server by using above cloned repo
>kubectl create -f kubernetes-metrics-server

>to list the resources details
kubectl top node
kubectl top pod

>to view the pod logs
kubectl logs -f pod-name

if we run multple containers within the pod then we can view the logs using
>kubectl logs -f pod-name -c container-name
